:"プロパティ"},{"text":"関数","id":"関数"},{"text":"イベント","id":"イベント"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性"},{"text":"Example extensions","id":"example_extensions"}],"summary":"このモジュールは拡張機能と、それを実行する環境についての情報を提供します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"runtime","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"runtime","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"runtime","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"runtime","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/mozilla/add-ons/webextensions/api/runtime","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/mozilla/add-ons/webextensions/api/runtime/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Mozilla","title":"Mozilla"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons","title":"アドオン"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions","title":"ブラウザー拡張機能"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API","title":"JavaScript API 群"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/runtime","title":"runtime"}],"pageTitle":"runtime - Mozilla | MDN","noIndexing":false}}